Package clinicalInformationSystem.model

Class THIModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • clinicalInformationSystem.model.THIModel
  • public class THIModel
extends java.lang.Object
    The Model for the Tinnitus Handicap Inventory(THI). It holds all the answers to the THI and also calculates the THI Score which indicates how Tinnitus handicaps a patient.
    Author:
    Team 9
